Set oven rack about 6 inches from the heat source and preheat the oven's broiler. Combine the whipped cream cheese and shredded habanero cheese. Place a dollop on each Snack Factory(R) Pretzel Crisps(R). Top with a few slices of bell pepper. Melt slightly under broiler or in a toaster oven. Top each with sweet chili sauce and another Pretzel Crisps(R).